snippet: Couples’ therapy is usually intended for two, but in “Psycho Therapy” the relationship in question is a moving target.
abstract: Daniel M Gold reviews Frank Strausser play Psycho Therapy at Cherry Lane Theater; Jan Leslie Harding and Angelica Page star.
